---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const withBase = (path: string): string => `${baseUrl}${path.replace(/^\/+/, '')}`;
---

<BaseLayout
  pageKey="about"
  title="O projektu - BL Prevoz | Javni prevoz Banja Luka"
  description="BL Prevoz je nezavisna, volonterski vođena platforma za informacije o javnom prevozu u Banjoj Luci. Red vožnje, linije i važne informacije na jednom mjestu."
  canonicalUrl="https://blprevoz.com/about/"
>
  <section class="section section--narrow" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section__title" id="about-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">O projektu</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">About</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="about-content">
        <!-- BHS version -->
        <div data-lang="bhs">
          <h2>Zašto BL Prevoz postoji?</h2>
          <p>
            Javni prevoz u Banjoj Luci obavlja više prevoznika, a informacije o linijama, redovima vožnje i cijenama karata često su raspoređene na različitim mjestima ili ih nije lako pronaći.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz je nastao iz potrebe da se te informacije objedine i učine dostupnim svima:
            jednostavno, pregledno i besplatno. Cilj platforme je da svaki korisnik brzo pronađe
            ono što mu je potrebno za kretanje gradom.
          </p>

          <h2>Šta možete uraditi na BL Prevozu?</h2>
          <div class="about-features">
            <a href={withBase('lines/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-route" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pregledajte autobuske linije i rute</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('lines/#timetable')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Provjerite red vožnje</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('pricing/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-ticket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pogledajte cijene karata</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('airport/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Informacije o aerodromskom transferu</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('updates/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pratite obavještenja o izmjenama</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <h2>Nezavisan projekat</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz <strong>nije zvanična stranica</strong> grada Banja Luka, prevoznika niti bilo koje institucije.
            Riječ je o nezavisnoj, volonterski vođenoj platformi koja nema komercijalnu pozadinu i ne zastupa interese nijednog prevoznika.
          </p>
          <p>
            Stranica je besplatna za korištenje i razvija se kao dio šire, takođe nezavisne inicijative otvorenih podataka u Bosni i Hercegovini,
            koja nije povezana sa državnim ili lokalnim institucijama, prevoznicima niti drugim organizacijama.
          </p>

          <h2>Odakle dolaze informacije?</h2>
          <p>
            Sve informacije na platformi prikupljene su iz:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>javno dostupnih podataka i izvora</li>
            <li>zvaničnih obavještenja prevoznika</li>
            <li>informacija koje objavljuju prevoznici i operateri</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Informacije prikazujemo na način koji je koristan korisnicima. Nastojimo da podaci budu tačni i ažurni,
            ali za najnovije izmjene uvijek preporučujemo dodatnu provjeru kod prevoznika.
          </p>

          <h2>Otvoreni podaci</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz se zasniva na principima otvorenih podataka. Podaci o javnom prevozu predstavljaju javni interes i trebalo bi da budu slobodno dostupni svima.
          </p>
          <p>
            Izvorni kod ovog projekta je javno dostupan, a podaci prikazani na sajtu mogu se slobodno koristiti u informativne svrhe.
            Nadamo se da ovaj pristup može podstaći i druge inicijative otvorenih podataka u našem gradu i šire.
          </p>

          <h2>Budući planovi</h2>
          <p>
            Platforma se i dalje razvija. Neka od planiranih unapređenja uključuju:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>ažuriranje i preciziranje lokacija autobusnih stajališta</li>
            <li>proširenje informacija o drugim vidovima prevoza</li>
            <li>unapređenje mape i dodavanje prikaza ruta autobusnih linija</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="about-cta">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div>
              <strong>Primijetili ste grešku ili imate prijedlog?</strong>
              <p>
                Pomozite da informacije budu što tačnije i korisnije.
                Ako ste primijetili netačan podatak ili imate prijedlog za poboljšanje,
                <a href={withBase('contact/')}>javite nam se</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- English version -->
        <div data-lang="en" style="display:none">
          <h2>Why does BL Prevoz exist?</h2>
          <p>
            Public transport in Banja Luka is provided by multiple operators, and information about routes, timetables, and ticket prices is often scattered across different sources or difficult to find.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz was created to bring that information together and make it accessible to everyone:
            simply, clearly, and free of charge. The platform's goal is to help every user quickly find
            what they need to move around the city.
          </p>

          <h2>What can you do on BL Prevoz?</h2>
          <div class="about-features">
            <a href={withBase('lines/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-route" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>View bus lines and routes</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('lines/#timetable')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Check timetables</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('pricing/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-ticket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>See ticket pricing</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('airport/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Airport transport information</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('updates/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Follow transport updates</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <h2>An independent project</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is <strong>not an official website</strong> of the City of Banja Luka, any transport operator, or any institution.
            It is an independent, volunteer-driven platform with no commercial backing and no affiliation with any transport company or public authority.
          </p>
          <p>
            The website is free to use and continues to be developed as part of a broader, likewise independent open data initiative in Bosnia and Herzegovina,
            which is not affiliated with government institutions, transport operators, or any organization.
          </p>

          <h2>Where does the information come from?</h2>
          <p>
            All information on the platform is gathered from:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>publicly available data and sources</li>
            <li>official operator announcements</li>
            <li>information published by transport operators</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We present information in a way that is useful for the public. We aim to keep it accurate and up to date,
            but we still recommend checking with operators for the latest changes.
          </p>

          <h2>Open data</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is guided by open data principles. Public transport information serves the public interest and should be freely available to everyone.
          </p>
          <p>
            The source code of this project is publicly available, and the data shown on the site may be freely used for informational purposes.
            We hope this approach can encourage similar open data initiatives in our city and beyond.
          </p>

          <h2>Future plans</h2>
          <p>
            The platform continues to evolve. Planned improvements include:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>updating and improving bus stop locations</li>
            <li>expanding information about other modes of transport</li>
            <li>improving the map and adding bus route visualization</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="about-cta">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div>
              <strong>Noticed an error or have a suggestion?</strong>
              <p>
                Help keep the information as accurate and useful as possible.
                If you've noticed incorrect data or have a suggestion,
                <a href={withBase('contact/')}>get in touch</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
